China 's Textile Production Dropping
BEIJING , November 30 ( Xinhua ) -- The latest figures from the State Statistics Bureau show that China 's textile production underwent a continuous decline in the first nine months this year .
The country produced 3.7 million tons of yarn between January and September , down 1.8 percent on an annual basis .
That of cloth was 12.7 billion meters , down six percent .
